Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:21.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But, never going back 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狼煙高く上げて Now dive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}煩悩なんてモノ Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}性懲りも無く Fight 仲間と
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I won't run away from my sin no more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:34.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}何処までも抗って Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:37.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 超えていく 恐れずに Bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm not afraid, bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:42.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if I'm drown in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:45.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分のチカラに変え Wipe out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 捻じ曲げる System
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:49.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never ever follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:56.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 立ち向かう and I'll defeat myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.37,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像人性一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.29,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你将凝视深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.28,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那里有七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.11,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}当你踏入其中 你会发觉自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.34,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}踏入未知领域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:58.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那些漂亮话 早就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让人得以为人的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:04.11,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总是伴随着我们 对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}致命的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.17,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.12,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不要转移视线 赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.57,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只是向前 向前 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.20,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必须再次取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}代价在不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.01,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使前方是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.72,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不再有任何后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:18.65,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坠落 坠落 堕入黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:21.20,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是 永远不回头 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.17,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}高举烽烟 然后潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.38,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}与烦恼说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.00,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惩前毖后 与伙伴一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.02,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}活着就是为了择日赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.70,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不再逃避我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:34.11,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我将一直抗争下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:37.70,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 无畏地超越 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.56,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不害怕 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:42.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使我将陷入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:45.56,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也要将其转化为我的力量 消除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 扭曲这个系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:49.12,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:56.29,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 我将面对挑战并战胜自己
