Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:20.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你在独自为何担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:23.40,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我明明在你的身旁
